{"tid":859516,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【離婚唔計】金獅花園321呎傳售420萬 低市價24%","createTime":"2018-10-12T14:37:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-12T23:13:09.000Z","uid":122377,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3a8366a3b56b083eb405d85717af23f5a86a45c7","tid":859516,"uid":122377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T14:37:14.000Z","msg":"市場瘋傳，大圍金獅花園金富閣中層戶，實用面積321方呎，單位一個半月前放盤叫價480萬元，已較市價約550萬元為低，有傳賣方是一對離婚夫婦，女方堅持劈價賣樓套現，遭另一方反對。消息指兩夫婦最終傾掂數，同意進一步劈價沽貨，單位傳最終以420萬元易手，呎價13,084元創屋苑去年10月後新低，低市價24%。金滿閣高層8室一個面積相同單位，今年8月造價560萬元，呎價17,445元。<br />\n<br />\n區內代理表示，近期業主情緒很恐慌，怕樓價會大跌，「最近睇咗幾個單位，業主都主動追返我問個客諗成點，好急咁款」。他又指，金獅花園好多業主都是很平買入，就算現在劈到400萬元，他們都不會肉赤。<br />\n<br />\n離婚唔計 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇下幾時玩到要穿400萬 先有承接 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"570f4c4efa63983ea08e9d77a2f80d84ab1bba93","tid":859516,"uid":41944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T14:44:44.000Z","msg":"唔肉赤，唔計<br />\n依家係入市好時機"},{"pid":"1490de4d5381e713a13f3f1ae773423ca19a1ac2","tid":859516,"uid":163207,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T15:05:56.000Z","msg":"青山道戴綠帽離婚計唔計?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31a20b6dd15974baf6ea860ae954ff2d7332dc7f","tid":859516,"uid":76563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T15:06:20.000Z","msg":"嘩 好抵喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e411492a9ca4acebc0afbb72933571bd5413640f","tid":859516,"uid":122377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1490de4d5381e713a13f3f1ae773423ca19a1ac2","tid":859516,"uid":163207,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T15:05:56.000Z","msg":"青山道戴綠帽離婚計唔計?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"